The critical notes make no pretension to completeness

They exhibit only the more important varieties of the best MSS, special prominence being given to those which bring out the comparative value of the different MSS, or which illustrate the kind of differences, whether as regards orthography or otherwise, which a student should learn to expect in comparing MSS. generally.
